  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU:</h1><p><br><br><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>THE LAST KING'S ACHER</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/279a8381a1b38297c520ff8cacb25546.poster.avif?t=1679761731\" width=700 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/279a8381a1b38297c520ff8cacb25546.webm?t=1679761731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/279a8381a1b38297c520ff8cacb25546.mp4?t=1679761731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Protect the King from evil creatures of a magic forest.<br><br><strong>The Gameplay</strong><br>Use you bow to protect the King! You have 3 main skills:<br><u>Flame Frenezy</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/82cccf5606c7e08239b97f093f1c16dc.poster.avif?t=1679761731\" width=700 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/82cccf5606c7e08239b97f093f1c16dc.webm?t=1679761731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/82cccf5606c7e08239b97f093f1c16dc.mp4?t=1679761731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>An arrow that evoques flame behind it burning everything in the way.<br><br><u>Thunder God</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/e38f65fe9756b7a52d2ef944833af9ae.poster.avif?t=1679761731\" width=700 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/e38f65fe9756b7a52d2ef944833af9ae.webm?t=1679761731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/e38f65fe9756b7a52d2ef944833af9ae.mp4?t=1679761731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Kill everyone on screen with this god-like thunder arrow.<br><br><u>A lot of Globins to Kill</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/ac7a0c5c2846de4adb62e1a3afbd6b1e.poster.avif?t=1679761731\" width=700 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/ac7a0c5c2846de4adb62e1a3afbd6b1e.webm?t=1679761731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1410260/extras/ac7a0c5c2846de4adb62e1a3afbd6b1e.mp4?t=1679761731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Thunder and Flame skills. You choose!<br>- Upgrade your skills to survive and get more points.<br>- Beautiful pixel graphics with carefully hand-drawn backgrounds;<br>- Captivating and  strange creatures born from this unique mysterious world.<br>- The controls are simple and accessible, but with several layers of depth to master;",
